{"name": "FoodCommune", "alternate_name": "", "description": "* If you can volunteer, please come for any hours between 10:00a-10:00p.
* If you can donate $30, to get 3 crates of food, come between 12:00-4:00p.
* If you can donate $10, to get 1 crate of food, come between 4:00-7:00.
* If you can donate just a couple of dollars, or are unable to donate at all due to financial hardship, come between 8:00p-12:00m.
* If you have livestock to feed or gardens to mulch, come between 8:00p-12:00m to get the leftovers.
* FoodCommune takes these 5 methods of payment: Cash, Cashapp, Venmo, PayPal, and Zelle.   (no plastic cards accepted)", "email": "", "url": "https://www.foodcommune.org/", "status": "active", "address": {"address_1": "368 Candler Road Southeast", "address_2": null, "city": "Atlanta", "state_province": "GA", "postal_code": "30317", "country": "US"}, "location": {"latitude": 33.7423911, "longitude": -84.2893048}, "phones": [{"number": "(404) 822-5685", "type": "voice"}], "regular_schedule": [{"weekday": "Saturday", "opens_at": "16:00", "closes_at": "23:00"}], "service_attributes": [{"attribute_key": "INFO", "attribute_value": "Needs volunteers"}, {"attribute_key": "INFO", "attribute_value": "Only serves surrounding neighborhood"}]}
